==评价==
《塞尔达传说 众神的三角力量》是超级任天堂最畅销的游戏之一。共在全球范围内售出461万份。<ref name="4mil">{{cite web | url=http://www.optigamer.com/news/?id=733 | title=Zelda sales charts and sequel announced | date=2004-03-28 | publisher=OptiGamer | author=Tenchi | accessdate=2005-12-03 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050223002315/http://www.optigamer.com/news/?id=733 | archivedate=2005-02-23 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>

《塞尔达传说 众神的三角力量》由于其图像和玩法在发行之时广受好评。2005年IGN编辑将其列为最佳100个游戏的第11位。<ref name="gamerankings">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/snes/588436-the-legend-of-zelda-a-link-to-the-past/index.html|title=The Legend of Zelda: A Link to the Past reviews|publisher=[[Game_Rankings|Game Rankings]]|accessdate=2007-03-07|archive-date=2014-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141230163506/http://www.gamerankings.com/snes/588436-the-legend-of-zelda-a-link-to-the-past/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Thomas, Lucas M.|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/01/23/the-legend-of-zelda-a-link-to-the-past-vc-review|title=The Legend of Zelda: A Link to the Past VC Review|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2007-03-20|archive-date=2012-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104071513/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/01/23/the-legend-of-zelda-a-link-to-the-past-vc-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>

